    {
      "id": "PopularPost257936",
      "post_content": "Actually a really cool idea. I would love to be able to make my Lotus Vale indestructible, but if a Terastodon, for example, enters the battlefield, then it easily can destroy this artifact first, and after this the land, that\u00b4s why I definitely rather go for Crucible of Worlds, instead of this.  \n  \nInstead of being able to give a creature +1/+1, they really should have made this artifact itself indestructible too. Apart from this, it\u00b4s pretty overcosted, anyway.",
